parties%20have%20an%20incredibly%20daunting%20task%20ahead%20of%20them.%20The%20agencies%20are%20much%20stronger%20enforcers%20than%20they%20were%20back%20in%202016.%20They%20are%20much%20more%20skeptical%20about%20some%20of%20the%20arguments%20that%20will%20be%20crucial%20to%20the%20merging%20parties%2C%20such%20as%20the%20role%20of%20efficiencies%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20David%20Balto%2C%20a%20consumer%20advocate%20and%20the%20former%20policy%20director%20of%20the%20Federal%20Trade%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EGiant%20insurers'%20past%20attempts%20to%20combine%20failed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EReports%20that%20Cigna%20and%20Humana%20want%20to%20pursue%20a%20merger%20are%20somewhat%20surprising%20given%20previous%20attempts%20between%20giant%20health%20insurers%20went%20up%20in%20flames%2C%20leading%20in%20one%20case%20to%20a%20prolonged%2C%20expensive%20legal%20battle.%20Still%2C%20Cigna%20and%20Humana%20did%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.modernhealthcare.com%2Farticle%2F20150811%2FNEWS%2F150819988%2Fhow-humana-hitched-with-aetna-and-drove-cigna-to-anthem%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Etoy%20with%20a%20deal%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20way%20back%20in%202014%20before%20they%20pursued%20deals%20with%20other%20partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20mid-2015%2C%20Cigna%20and%20Anthem%20said%20they%20would%20pair%20up%20in%20a%20%2454%20billion%20deal%2C%20while%20Aetna%20and%20Humana%20sought%20a%20%2437-billion%20tie-up.%20But%20federal%20judges%20blocked%20both%20proposed%20mergers%20in%202017%20after%20they%20were%20challenged%20by%20the%20Justice%20Department%20for%20threatening%20to%20harm%20competition%20in%20various%20insurance%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECigna%20and%20Anthem%20sued%20each%20other%20for%20billions%2C%20each%20arguing%20that%20the%20other%20had%20sabotaged%20the%20deal.%20Years%20later%2C%20in%202020%2C%20a%20Delaware%20court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.modernhealthcare.com%2Finsurance%2Fanthem-cigna-cant-collect-billions-damages-over-failed-merger%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eruled%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20neither%20of%20the%20companies%20could%20recover%20any%20damages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20to%20sidestep%20antitrust%20scrutiny%2C%20health%20insurers%20eyed%20mergers%20with%20other%20pieces%20of%20the%20healthcare%20system%20outside%20of%20insurance.%20In%202018%2C%20Cigna%20combined%20with%20the%20pharmacy-benefit%20manager%20Express%20Scripts%20and%20pharmacy%20chain%20CVS%20Health%20bought%20Aetna.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHumana%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20pushed%20deeper%20into%20providing%20care%20directly%20to%20patients%20by%20acquiring%20home-health%20company%20Kindred%20and%20building%20primary-care%20clinics%20for%20seniors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECigna%20and%20Humana%20would%20face%20a%20more%20skeptical%20Justice%20Department%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAny%20deal%20between%20health%20insurers%20the%20size%20of%20Cigna%20and%20Humana%20would%20have%20to%20get%20past%20the%20Justice%20Department's%20antitrust%20enforcers.%20That's%20not%20going%20to%20be%20easy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20are%20health-insurance%20markets%20already%20heavily%20consolidated%2C%20but%20antitrust%20enforcers%20under%20the%20Biden%20Administration%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.statnews.com%2F2023%2F07%2F19%2Fantitrust-scrutiny-health-care%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eadopted%20a%20more%20aggressive%20stance%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20toward%20all%20types%20of%20healthcare%20mergers%20in%20the%20past%20year.%20The%20FTC%20has%20also%20dialed%20up%20scrutiny%20of%20PBMs%2C%20and%20though%20the%20Justice%20Department%20likely%20would%20review%20an%20insurance%20merger%2C%20the%20two%20agencies%20often%20work%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBalto%20said%20the%20Justice%20Department%20is%20%26quot%3Bvastly%20more%20sensitive%26quot%3B%20to%20whether%20mergers%20will%20harm%20consumers%20and%20healthcare%20providers%2C%20whereas%20in%20the%20past%20it%20focused%20on%20a%20merger's%20impact%20on%20businesses%20such%20as%20employers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhealthpolicy.duke.edu%2Fpeople%2Fbarak-richman-phd%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EBarak%20Richman%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20law%20professor%20at%20Duke%20University%2C%20said%20that%20traditionally%2C%20antitrust%20enforcers%20took%20a%20narrow%20view%20of%20harm%2C%20scrutinizing%20overlap%20between%20businesses%20in%20specific%20geographic%20markets.%20But%20he%20said%20there's%20now%20a%20greater%20appetite%20to%20challenge%20mergers%20based%20on%20%26quot%3Bmore%20expansive%20theories%20of%20harm.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20are%20two%20large%20health-insurance%20companies.%20They%20offer%20insurance%20products%20all%20over%20the%20country.%20They%20engage%20with%20providers%20all%20over%20the%20country.%20They%20both%20have%20PBMs%20and%20provide%20pharmaceutical%20benefits%20all%20over%20the%20country.%20The%20analysis%20has%20to%20have%20a%20more%20wide-angle%20lens.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.commonwealthfund.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fdocuments%2F___media_files_publications_issue_brief_2015_nov_1845_dafny_impact_hlt_ins_industry_consolidation_ib.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EResearch%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20shown%20that%20when%20insurers%20merge%2C%20health-plan%20premiums%20increase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20insurers%20may%20argue%20that%20they%20have%20little%20overlap%20between%20their%20businesses.%20Already%2C%20Cigna%20is%20considering%20selling%20its%20small%20Medicare%20Advantage%20business%2C%20Reuters%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fmarkets%2Fdeals%2Fcigna-explores-shedding-medicare-advantage-business-sources-2023-11-06%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DNEW%2520YORK%252C%2520Nov%25206%2520(Reuters%2Cpeople%2520familiar%2520with%2520the%2520matter.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20this%20month.%20And%20Humana%20in%20February%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpress.humana.com%2Fnews%2Fnews-details%2F2023%2FHumana-to-Exit-Employer-Group-Commercial-Medical-Products-Business%2Fdefault.aspx%23gsc.tab%3D0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esaid%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20was%20getting%20out%20of%20the%20commercial-insurance%20business%20over%20the%20next%2018%20to%2024%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Matthew%20Cantor%2C%20an%20antitrust%20expert%20and%20partner%20at%20the%20law%20firm%20Constantine%20Cannon%2C%20said%20divestitures%20aren't%20always%20a%20sure%20fix.%20He%20pointed%20to%20the%20failed%20merger%20attempt%20between%20Aetna%20and%20Humana%2C%20in%20which%20the%20court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.healthaffairs.org%2Fcontent%2Fforefront%2Fcourt-blocks-aetna-humana-deal-mega-mergers-meet-trump-administration-next%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Edetermined%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Aetna's%20plan%20to%20sell%20Medicare%20Advantage%20plans%20to%20Molina%20wouldn't%20help%20replace%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20of%20this%20comes%20down%20to%20not%20only%20are%20they%20going%20to%20divest%2C%20but%20who's%20going%20to%20buy%20it%3F%26quot%3B%20Cantor%20said.%20%26quot%3BAre%20they%20a%20vibrant%20competitor%3F%20Or%20is%20it%20going%20to%20be%20that%20someone's%20going%20to%20buy%20this%20and%20not%20know%20how%20to%20run%20it%20and%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20run%20to%20the%20ground%2C%20and%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%20you're%20going%20to%20be%20left%20with%20a%20more%20powerful%20Cigna.%20That's%20going%20to%20be%20the%20question.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcigna-humana-merger-antitrust-scrutiny-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701369966000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6568ca0058e7c0c29a285993%3Fforma