on%20has%20committed%20to%20reaching%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.imo.org%2Fen%2FMediaCentre%2FHotTopics%2FPages%2FCutting-GHG-emissions.aspx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Enet-zero%20emissions%20by%202050%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20a%20recent%20analysis%20suggests%20the%20industry%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcms.globalmaritimeforum.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FGTZ_ClimateActionInShipping2023.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Estruggling%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20take%20steps%20toward%20that%20goal%2C%20including%20using%20zero-emission%20options%20for%205%25%20of%20its%20fuels%20by%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shipping%20giant%20AP%20Moller-Maersk%20and%20its%20parent%20company%2C%20AP%20Moller%20Holding%2C%20this%20year%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.c2xglobal.com%2Fnews%2Fc2x-to-build-large-scale-green-methanol-production-for-multiple-industries%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Efounded%20a%20subsidiary%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20green-methanol%20production.%20But%20sources%20of%20green%20methanol%20are%20limited%2C%20and%20even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F10%2F30%2Fbusiness%2Feconomy%2Fshipping-climate-change-green-fuel.html%3Flogin%3Demail%26auth%3Dlogin-email%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EMaersk's%20CEO%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20said%20methanol%20won't%20be%20a%20silver%20bullet%20for%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20using%20biofuels%20and%20green%20methanol%2C%20Maersk%20is%20also%20relying%20on%20software%20to%20help%20it%20reduce%20emissions.%20The%20company%20told%20Business%20Insider%20it%20had%20grown%20its%20IT%20department%20to%20almost%206%2C000%20software%20engineers%20from%20fewer%20than%202%2C000%20in%20four%20years%2C%20largely%20to%20scale%20up%20its%20customer-facing%20logistics%20platforms%2C%20streamline%20its%20ship%20operations%2C%20and%20reach%20its%20sustainability%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20representative%20for%20Maersk%20said%20strategies%20to%20make%20the%20company's%20ships%20sail%20more%20efficiently%20are%20part%20of%20Maersk's%20calculation%20for%20reaching%20net%20zero.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20progress%20toward%20getting%20zero-emission%20fuels%20aboard%20lags%2C%20engineers%20and%20startups%20working%20with%20digital%20technology%20are%20hoping%20to%20fill%20the%20gap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EAutonomous%20tech%20and%20AI%20can%20help%20streamline%20sailing%20and%20cut%20fuel%20costs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20startups%20across%20the%20world%20have%20started%20tackling%20autonomous%20shipping.%20Companies%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Funleash-future-boats.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EUnleash%20Future%20Boats%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fseafar.eu%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ESeafar%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20working%20on%20unmanned%20waterborne%20trucks%20operating%20in%20ports%20and%20partially%20or%20fully%20remote-controlled%20ships%20operating%20along%20rivers%20and%20coasts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%20Johnson%2C%20a%20marine%20engineer%20who%20was%20formerly%20an%20executive%20at%20companies%20including%20Crowley%20Maritime%2C%20said%20he%20founded%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsea-machines.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ESea%20Machines%20Robotics%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202016%20after%20realizing%20the%20industry%20needed%20to%20push%20beyond%20the%20manual%20technologies%20of%20the%2020th%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20only%20time%20the%20maritime%20industry%20is%20ever%20on%20the%20front%20page%20of%20a%20paper%20is%20when%20there's%20an%20accident.%20But%20there's%20much%20more%20to%20us%20than%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Johnson%2C%20who's%20also%20Sea%20Machines'%20CEO%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Headshot%20of%20Michael%20Johnson%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655e96dd9c7d23cb3b9f1d0e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22540%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMichael%20Johnson%2C%20the%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Sea%20Machines%20Robotics.%3Cp%3ESea%20Machines%20Robotics%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESea%20Machines%20has%20raised%20more%20than%20%2440%20million%20so%20far%20to%20develop%20products%20including%20an%20AI-based%20computer%20vision%20sensor%20for%20ships.%20It%20also%20aims%20to%20give%20boats%20a%20self-pilot%20option%20via%20an%20autonomous%20control%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESea%20Machines%20has%20its%20autonomous%20control%20systems%20integrated%20in%20smaller%20workboats%2C%20and%20Johnson%20said%20it%20plans%20to%20introduce%20them%20to%20larger%20fleets%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20person%20sits%20and%20looks%20at%20the%20Sea%20Machines%20Robotics'%20AI-based%20computer%20vision%20sensor%20for%20ships.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655e9bc84ca513d8242df827%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESea%20Machines%20Robotics%20developed%20an%20AI-based%20computer%20vision%20sensor%20for%20ships.%3Cp%3ESea%20Machines%20Robotics%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJohnson%20said%20he%20saw%20that%20decarbonization%20was%20not%20only%20a%20bonus%20of%20Sea%20Machines'%20technology%20but%20its%20best%20value%20proposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20because%20Sea%20Machines'%20system%20is%20directly%20connected%20to%20a%20ship's%20propulsion%20system%2C%20it%20can%20control%20fuel%20use%20better%20than%20a%20human%20operator%20could.%20Recent%20research%20suggests%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS0029801823008041%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enext-generation%20autonomous%20ships%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20help%20cut%20carbon%20emissions%20by%20about%2010%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222135%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20control%20room%20team%20in%20the%20US%20monitors%20(and%20celebrates)%20the%20progress%20of%20a%20workboat%20traveling%20around%20Denmark%20using%20Sea%20Machines%20Robotics'%20autonomous%20self-piloting%20system.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6556255622cf74a573984f77%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221300%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Sea%20Machines%20Robotics%20team%20can%20monitor%20(and%20celebrate)%20autonomous%20vessel%20operations%20from%20a%20control%20room.%3Cp%3ESea%20Machines%20Robotics%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you're%20burning%20a%20hundred%20tons%20of%20fuel%20a%20day%20that%20costs%20%24650%20a%20ton%2C%20it's%20significant%20savings%2C%26quot%3B%20Johnson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20market%20where%20biofuels%20and%20synthetic%20fuels%20can%20cost%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iea.org%2Fdata-and-statistics%2Fcharts%2Findicative-shipping-fuel-cost-ranges%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eat%20least%20twice%20as%20much%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20fossil%20fuels%2C%20Johnson%20said%20he%20hopes%20that%20fuel%20savings%20from%20autonomy%20can%20help%20encourage%20the%20uptake%20of%20zero-emission%20fuels%20required%20by%20the%20industry's%20net-zero%20ambitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ENew%20control%20systems%20and%20interfaces%20can%20help%20crews%20optimize%20operations%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20an%20industry%20with%20over%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Functad.org%2Fsystem%2Ffiles%2Fofficial-document%2Frmt2022ch2_en.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E100%2C000%20vessels%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20decarbonization%20will%20take%20effort%20from%20a%20variety%20of%20companies%20and%20technologies.%20These%20companies%20are%20primarily%20exploring%20green%20energy%20from%20ammonia%2C%20nuclear%20reactions%2C%20and%20wind%2C%20as%20well%20as%20technology%20like%20AI-powered%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deepsea.ai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eroute-optimization%20software%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20more%20technologies%20are%20introduced%2C%20a%20ship's%20operator%20has%20to%20take%20in%20more%20information%20and%20act%20on%20it.%20Johnson%20said%20an%20autonomous%20system%20could%20help%20manage%20the%20output%20from%20optimization%20apps%20and%20alleviate%20information%20overload.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20much%20like%20what%20you%20see%20in%20the%20very%20efficient%20distribution%20networks%20like%20Amazon%20distribution%20network%2C%20where%20they've%20tied%20their%20robots%20to%20their%20logistics%20software%2C%20enabling%20an%20immense%20amount%20of%20productivity%2C%26quot%3B%20Johnson%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20we%20can%20do%20that%20on%20the%20oceans%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20startup%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsmart-ship.eu%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ESmart-Ship%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20taking%20a%20similar%20approach.%20Rather%20than%20automating%20certain%20parts%20of%20the%20voyage%2C%20Smart-Ship%20aims%20to%20recommend%20the%20safest%20or%20most%20efficient%20controls%20for%20an%20operator%20to%20use%20at%20a%20given%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmart-Ship%20offers%20what's%20called%20a%20force-feedback%20lever%20%E2%80%94%20essentially%20a%20high-tech%20version%20of%20the%20joysticks%20that%20control%20a%20ship's%20throttle%2C%20thrust%2C%20and%20rotation.%20The%20company%20has%20sold%20a%20little%20over%20100%20of%20them%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221911%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Smart-Ship's%20force-feedback%20lever.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655626fc4ca513d8242a6f99%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221505%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESmart-Ship's%20%26quot%3BThrottle%20%26amp%3B%20Bow%20Buster%26quot%3B%20is%20one%20of%20three%20force-feedback%20levers%20they%20offer%20to%20help%20ships%20increase%20safety%20and%20fuel%20savings.%3Cp%3ESmart-Ship%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20traditional%20levers%20are%20static%2C%20Smart-Ship's%20version%20is%20designed%20to%20use%20subtle%20movements%20or%20resistance%20to%20signal%20to%20an%20operator%20to%20reduce%20throttle%20when%20approaching%20an%20object%2C%20steer%20away%20when%20approaching%20shallow%20water%2C%20or%20change%20speed%20when%20there's%20an%20option%20to%20use%20fuel%20more%20efficiently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20really%20need%20to%20rethink%20the%20way%20they're%20sailing%20ships%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jelle%20Tiemensma%2C%20Smart-Ship's%20cofounder%20and%20chief%20technology%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222475%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Headshot%20of%20Jelle%20Tiemensma%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655e97614ca513d8242df803%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221856%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJelle%20Tiemensma%2C%20the%20cofounder%20and%20CTO%20of%20Smart-Ship%3Cp%3ESmart-Ship%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20these%20companies%20don't%20imagine%20that%20large%20ships%20will%20be%20fully%20unmanned%20anytime%20soon%2C%20they're%20betting%20that%20advanced%20software%20and%20intuitive%20interfaces%20can%20help%20crew%20members%20sail%20more%20sustainably.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20industry%20needs%20more%20collaboration%20and%20digital%20connectivity%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESofia%20F%C3%BCrstenberg%20Stott%2C%20a%20sustainability%20consultant%20for%20industry%20stakeholders%20such%20as%20ship%20owners%2C%20manufacturers%2C%20and%20insurance%20companies%2C%20said%20that%20so%20far%20the%20industry's%20sustainability%20projects%20have%20been%20small-scale%2C%20like%20pilot%20programs%20for%20new%20maritime%20tech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20yet%20in%20the%20scale-up%20phase%20where%20we%20have%20established%20the%20business%20models%20and%20the%20new%20working%20environment%2C%26quot%3B%20Stott%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222279%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sofia%20F%C3%BCrstenberg%20Stott%20headshot%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655620e422cf74a573984ce5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222449%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESofia%20F%C3%BCrstenberg%20Stott%2C%20a%20sustainability%20consultant%20for%20maritime%20industry%20stakeholders.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Sofia%20F%C3%BCrstenberg%20Stott%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20move%20beyond%20that%2C%20Stott%20said%2C%20companies%20need%20to%20come%20together%20to%20create%20a%20plan%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sustainableshipping.org%2Froadmap%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ESustainable%20Shipping%20Initiative's%20Roadmap%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20prod%20them%20to%20actually%20take%20steps%20toward%20net-zero%20emissions%20by%202050.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20benefit%20may%20not%20be%20a%20benefit%20that%20you%20can%20count%20in%20dollars%20next%20year%2C%20or%20even%20five%20years%20from%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Stott%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20it's%20about%20staying%20sustainable%20for%20the%20long%20term.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMikael%20Lind%2C%20a%20research%20advisor%20specializing%20in%20maritime%20informatics%20at%20the%20Research%20Institutes%20of%20Sweden%2C%20said%20one%20of%20the%20shipping%20industry's%20obstacles%20to%20decarbonization%20is%20a%20lack%20of%20digital%20connectivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20understand%20the%20deviation%20between%20plan%20and%20the%20actual%20outcome%2C%26quot%3B%20Lind%20said.%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20aviation%20sector%2C%20this%20is%20rather%20simple%2C%20because%20if%20you're%20up%20in%20the%20air%20you%20have%20flight%20trackers%20and%20you%20know%20that%20the%20plane%20needs%20to%20be%20down%20on%20the%20ground%20pretty%20soon%2C%20otherwise%20it%20would%20crash.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222996%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Headshot%20of%20Mikael%20Lind%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6556227e22cf74a573984d99%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223292%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMikael%20Lind%2C%20a%20senior%20research%20advisor%20specializing%20in%20maritime%20informatics%20at%20the%20Research%20Institutes%20of%20Sweden.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Mikael%20Lind%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20with%20boats%2C%20data%20isn't%20always%20available%20for%20cargo%20owners%20to%20track%20their%20shipments.%20Storms%20or%20alternate%20routes%20can%20cause%20multiday%20delays.%20And%20when%20ships%20arrive%20at%20a%20busy%20port%2C%20they%20may%20need%20to%20idle%20for%20days%20to%20wait%20for%20an%20open%20spot%20to%20unload.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELind%20and%20his%20team%20are%20working%20with%20industry%20partners%20like%20the%20port%20operator%20PSA%20International%20to%20pilot%20a%20data-sharing%20initiative%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvirtualwatchtower.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Evirtual%20watchtowers%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20better%20keep%20an%20eye%20on%20disruptions%20in%20the%20supply%20chain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20industry%20is%20working%20on%20logistics%20technologies%20to%20help%20achieve%20so-called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgreenvoyage2050.imo.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F01%2FGIA-just-in-time-hires.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ejust-in-time%20arrivals%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20By%20slightly%20slowing%20their%20routes%20in%20order%20to%20arrive%20at%20a%20port%20only%20when%20there's%20an%20open%20spot%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmaritime-executive.com%2Feditorials%2Fpartnering-towards-zero-emissions-shipping-playbook-part-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eships