ommittees%20in%20the%20United%20States%20Senate%2C%26quot%3B%20Sen.%20John%20Cornyn%2C%20a%20Texas%20Republican%2C%20said%20after%20Durbin%20tried%20to%20curtail%20Republicans%20from%20speaking%20on%20unrelated%20judicial%20nominations%20that%20appeared%20to%20be%20designed%20to%20delay%20the%20subpoena%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESen.%20Lindsey%20Graham%2C%20the%20top%20Republican%20on%20the%20panel%2C%20blasted%20Durbin's%20action%2C%20warning%20that%20the%20panel%20could%20now%20go%20after%20private%20individuals%20at%20its%20will.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20political%20effort%20by%20the%20radical%20effort%20to%20destroy%20this%20court%2C%26quot%3B%20Graham%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20subpoenaed%20two%20prominent%2C%20conservative%20people.%20You%20have%20ignored%20other%20problems%20within%20the%20court%20%E2%80%A6%20this%20raw%20politics%2C%20this%20dangerous%20politics%2C%20and%20this%20committee%20is%20taking%20the%20country%20down%20a%20very%20dangerous%20road.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDurbin%20has%20long%20vowed%20to%20press%20on%20with%20requiring%20Crow%20and%20Leo%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20Senate's%20demands%20after%20the%20pair%20refused%20to%20do%20so.%20Crow%20has%20been%20in%20the%20news%20for%20months%20related%20to%20his%20friendship%20to%20Justice%20Clarence%20Thomas.%20ProPublica%20uncovered%20numerous%20trips%20and%20gifts%20Crow%20lavished%20on%20the%20justice%20and%20his%20family%2C%20which%20Thomas%20often%20did%20not%20list%20on%20his%20financial%20disclosure.%20Leo%20organized%20a%20lavish%20fishing%20trip%20with%20Justice%20Samuel%20Alito%2C%20which%20was%20attended%20by%20Paul%20Singer%2C%20a%20conservative%20billionaire%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjustice-samuel-alito-admits-to-luxury-fishing-trip-paul-singer-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewho%20later%20had%20cases%20before%20the%20the%20high%20court.%20%3C%2Fa%3EThomas%20and%20Alito%20have%20denied%20any%20wrongdoing