-palestinian-protesters-clash-in-nyc-unfurl-swastika-in-rockefeller-center%2Famp_articleshow%2F105635390.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fpro-palestinian-protesters-clash-in-nyc-unfurl-swastika-in-rockefeller-center%2Famp_articleshow%2F105635390.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20to%20watch%20at%20COP28%20Dubai%2C%20the%20UN%20climate%20summit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228640%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22COP28%20President%20Sultan%20Al%20Jaber%20walks%20through%20the%20venue%20ahead%20of%20the%20UN%20Climate%20Summit%20in%20Dubai%2C%20United%20Arab%20Emirates.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65685d9586933e8fdb2e3fe8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225760%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECOP28%20President%20Sultan%20Al%20Jaber%20walks%20through%20the%20venue%20ahead%20of%20the%20UN%20climate%20summit%20in%20Dubai%2C%20United%20Arab%20Emirates.%3Cp%3EPeter%20Dejong%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EUnited%20Arab%20Emirates%2C%20a%20wealthy%20petrostate%2C%20is%20hosting%20this%20year's%20UN%20climate%20summit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECountries%20will%20debate%20cutbacks%20to%20burning%20fossil%20fuels%20and%20climate%20funding%20for%20poorer%20countries.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOn%20the%20first%20day%2C%20countries%20agreed%20to%20some%20rules%20for%20the%20loss%20and%20damage%20fund.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThis%20article%20is%20part%20of%20Insider's%20weekly%20newsletter%20on%20sustainability.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsubscription%2Fnewsletter%2Finsider-sustainability%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESign%20up%20here%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDUBAI%2C%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%94%20There's%20always%20one%20big%20question%20heading%20into%20the%20UN's%20annual%20climate%20conference%3A%20What%20would%20success%20look%20like%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20major%20themes%20emerged%20ahead%20of%20the%20two-week%20event%20that%20kicks%20off%20today%20in%20Dubai%2C%20where%20some%2070%2C000%20climate%20diplomats%2C%20nongovernmental%20organizations%2C%20activists%2C%20and%20reporters%20from%20around%20the%20world%20are%20expected%20to%20gather.%20The%20central%20tension%20is%20whether%20this%20year's%20host%20%E2%80%94%20a%20wealthy%20petrostate%20whose%20largest%20exports%20are%20oil%20and%20natural%20gas%20%E2%80%94%20can%20corral%20nearly%20200%20other%20participating%20nations%20toward%20cutting%20back%20on%20the%20fossil%20fuels%20that%20are%20largely%20driving%20the%20climate%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20appointed%20Sultan%20Al%20Jaber%2C%20the%20head%20of%20the%20state-owned%20oil%20company%20Adnoc%2C%20to%20preside%20over%20the%20summit.%20He's%20also%20the%20CEO%20of%20Masdar%2C%20a%20state-owned%20renewable-energy%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClimate%20advocates%20say%20that%20Al%20Jaber's%20role%20as%20a%20fossil-fuel%20executive%20is%20a%20conflict%20of%20interest.%20Documents%20obtained%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcop28-host-uae-broker-secret-oil-deals-climate-summit-bbc-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ECentre%20for%20Climate%20Reporting%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fscience-environment-67508331%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Efirst%20reported%20by%20the%20BBC%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20suggest%20those%20concerns%20might%20not%20be%20misplaced.%20The%20documents%20list%20talking%20points%20for%20Emirati%20officials%20meeting%20with%20other%20countries%20ahead%20of%20COP28%20and%20include%20the%20promotion%20of%20oil%20and%20gas%20deals%2C%20as%20well%20as%20renewable-energy%20deals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAl%20Jaber%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrnKMhK-cP8U%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eduring%20a%20press%20conference%20Wednesday%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20he%20never%20saw%20the%20talking%20points%20or%20used%20them%20in%20his%20discussions%2C%20characterizing%20the%20report%20as%20%26quot%3Bfalse%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bincorrect.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20meeting%20I%20have%20conducted%20with%20every%20government%2C%20or%20any%20other%20stakeholder%2C%20has%20always%20been%20centered%20around%20one%20thing%20and%20one%20thing%20only%2C%20and%20that%20is%20my%20COP28%20agenda%20and%20how%20we%20can%20collectively%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%20ever%2C%20adopt%20a%20mindset%20that%20is%20centered%20around%20implementation%20and%20action%20to%20keep%201.5%20within%20reach%2C%26quot%3B%20Al%20Jaber%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20referring%20to%20the%20Paris%20agreement's%20goal%20to%20limit%20global%20warming%20to%201.5%20degrees%20Celsius%20by%202030%2C%20compared%20with%20preindustrial%20levels.%20Climate%20scientists%20say%20that%20surpassing%20this%20threshold%20would%20cause%20catastrophes%2C%20including%20more%20extreme%20wildfires%2C%20droughts%2C%20hurricanes%2C%20and%20floods.%20People%20are%20already%20facing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-climate-change-crisis-extreme-weather-is-costing-you-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20consequences%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20climate%20crisis%2C%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flast-three-months-on-earth-were-the-hottest-on-record-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Edeadly%20heat%20waves%20this%20year%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20being%20just%20one%20example.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20the%20world%20isn't%20doing%20enough%20to%20hold%20warming%20to%201.5%20degrees%3B%20indeed%2C%20the%20planet%20has%20already%20warmed%20nearly%201.2%20degrees%20Celsius%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unep.org%2Fresources%2Femissions-gap-report-2023%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20UN%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Countries%20need%20to%20slash%20greenhouse-gas%20emissions%20by%2042%25%20in%20the%20coming%20years%20to%20stay%20on%20track.%20This%20is%20partly%20why%20this%20year's%20conference%20is%20so%20important.%20For%20the%20first%20time%2C%20there%20will%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bglobal%20stocktake%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20UN%20speak%20for%20a%20climate%20report%20card.%20We%20already%20know%20countries%20aren't%20cutting%20emissions%20fast%20enough%2C%20but%20in%20Dubai%2C%20leaders%20could%20agree%20on%20how%20to%20close%20the%20gap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAl%20Jaber%20outlined%20a%20lot%20of%20priorities%20that%20would%20help%3A%20tripling%20renewable-energy%20capacity%2C%20fast-tracking%20energy%20efficiency%20across%20industries%2C%20and%20a%20%26quot%3Bphasedown%26quot%3B%20of%20fossil%20fuels.%20He%20also%20emphasized%20the%20need%20for%20wealthy%20countries%20to%20make%20good%20on%20their%20promises%20to%20finance%20climate%20action%20in%20poorer%20nations%20and%20work%20out%20the%20details%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bloss%20and%20damage%26quot%3B%20fund%20to%20help%20those%20nations%20rebuild%20after%20climate-fueled%20disasters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20already%20was%20an%20early%20win%20on%20that%20front%20during%20the%20opening%20ceremony%20on%20Thursday.%20Countries%20agreed%20to%20some%20overarching%20rules%20for%20the%20loss%20and%20damage%20fund%3A%20It%20will%20temporarily%20be%20run%20by%20the%20World%20Bank%2C%20contributions%20are%20voluntary%2C%20and%20the%20money%20can%20come%20from%20both%20the%20public%20and%20private%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20fund%20doesn't%20an%20overarching%20financial%20goal.%20A%20UN-commissioned%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lse.ac.uk%2Fgranthaminstitute%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2FIHLEG-Finance-for-Climate-Action-1.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%2