parties%20will%20get%200-2.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20predictions%20by%20TV%209%20Bharatvarsh-Polstrat%20swing%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Congress%2C%20however%2C%20with%20the%20party%20being%20projected%20to%20win%20between%20111%20and%20121%20seats%20and%20the%20BJP%20being%20restricted%20to%20106-116.%20The%20constituencies%20where%20other%20parties%20are%20projected%20to%20win%20are%20between%20zero%20and%20six.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20poll%20by%20Dainik%20Bhaskar%20has%20also%20given%20a%20slight%20edge%20to%20the%20Congress%2C%20predicting%20that%20the%20party%20will%20win%20105-120%20seats%20while%20the%20BJP%20is%20expected%20to%20win%20between%2095%20and%20115%20seats.%20The%20number%20for%20other%20parties%20is%20also%20quite%20high%2C%20between%200%20and%2015%2C%20indicating%20that%20they%20may%20have%20a%20role%20to%20play%20if%20the%20BJP%20or%20the%20Congress%20fall%20short%20of%20a%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20and%20BJP%20also%20seem%20neck-and-neck%20according%20to%20the%20Times%20Now%20ETG%20poll%2C%20with%20the%20former%20having%20a%20slight%20advantage.%20The%20exit%20poll%20has%20predicted%20109-125%20seats%20for%20the%20Congress%20and%20between%20105%20and%20117%20for%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJan%20Ki%20Baat%20has%20the%20closest%20prediction%20in%20its%20exit%20poll%2C%20with%20the%20numbers%20indicating%20that%20the%20results%20could%20go%20either%20way.%20It%20has%20projected%20102-125%20seats%20for%20the%20Congress%2C%20100-123%20for%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20and%20five%20for%20Others.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20campaign%20has%20been%20led%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20the%20party%20has%20avoided%20giving%20a%20clear%20answer%20on%20whether%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20will%20be%20the%20chief%20minister%20if%20it%20wins%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20The%20party%20has%20also%20fielded%20seven%20MPs%2C%20including%20union%20ministers%20Narendra%20Singh%20T