C%20and%20the%20Congress%20no%20more%20than%2095.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20exit%20polls%20that%20might%20give%20the%20Congress%20some%20hope%20are%20India%20Today-My%20Axis%20and%20India%20TV-CNX%2C%20although%20even%20India%20Today%20gave%20the%20BJP%20an%20upper%20margin%20of%20100%20seats%20and%2086-106%20for%20the%20ruling%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20Today%20gave%20the%20Congress%2094-104%20seats%2C%20with%20the%20BJP%20just%20marginally%20behind%20at%2080-90.%20Significantly%2C%20these%20(and%20TV9%20Bharatvarsh)%20are%20the%20only%20exit%20polls%20to%20give%20the%20Congress%20over%20100%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHealth%20Warning%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EExit%20polls%20often%20get%20it%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENDTV's%20Pre-Poll%20Survey%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pre-poll%20survey%20gave%20the%20PM%20a%20five%20per%20cent%20lead%20over%20Mr%20Gehlot%20in%20the%20battle%20of%20big%20names%2C%20suggesting%20the%20BJP%20had%20an%20edge.%20While%20that%20seems%20to%20be%20the%20case%20-%20based%20on%20exit%20polls%20-%20the%20Congress%20will%20take%20heart%20from%20the%20fact%20only%2024%20per%20cent%20of%20respondents%20were%20dissatisfied%20with%20their%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frajasthan-assembly-election-ndtv-opinion-poll-modi-factor-to-give-bjp-edge-in-rajasthan-ndtvs-opinion-poll-says-4542259%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E'Modi%20Factor'%20To%20Give%20BJP%20Edge%20In%20Rajasthan%3F%20NDTV's%20Opinion%20Poll%20Says...%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20survey%20of%20over%203%2C000%20people%20-%20across%2030%20of%20Rajasthan's%20200%20Assembly%20constituencies%20over%20a%20week%20starting%20October%2024%20-%20threw%20up%20a%20mixed%20bag%20of%20results%2C%20giving%20the%20ruling%20Congress%20a%20thumbs-up%20on%20some%20issues%2C%20such%20as%20state-run%20schools%20and%20hospitals%2C%20and%20handin