e-set-up%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eformal%20indictment%20issued%20in%20a%20New%20York%20court%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cspan%3Eagainst%20an%20Indian%20national%20and%20an%20%E2%80%98identified%20Indian%20government%20employee%E2%80%99%2C%20among%20others%2C%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fpannun-assassination-plot-india-enquiry-committee-set-up%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eplotting%20the%20murder%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cspan%3Eof%20a%20US%20citizen%20active%20in%20the%20Khalistan%20movement%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eare%20extremely%20damaging%20to%20the%20reputation%20of%20the%20country%20and%20those%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20national%20security.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWithout%20getting%20into%20the%20legal%20details%20of%20the%20indictment%20and%20the%20case%20itself%20(for%20details%20see%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fnijjar-pannun-modi-foreign-policy-national-interest%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehere%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E)%2C%20it%20is%20vital%20to%20contextualise%20the%20impact%20it%20can%20have%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findias-abstention-in-un-gaza-truce-vote-reflects-amoral-apathetic-exceptionalism%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20global%20moral%20stature%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20foreign%20policy-security%20outlook.%20The%20current%20Indian%20government%20has%20aggressively%20pursued%20a%20policy%20of%20narrative%20control%20to%20please%20and%20project%20an%20image%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98global%20moral%20power%E2%80%99%20and%20%3Cem%3EVishwaguru%3C%2Fem%3E%20(world%20leader)%20under%20Modi%20across%20each%20multilateral%20and%20plurilateral%20summit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMore%20often%20than%20not%2C%20it%20is%20authoritarian%20countries%20like%20Russia%2C%20China%20or%20North%20Korea%20which%20are%20in%20the%20news%20for%20alleged%20crimes%20conducted%20on%20foreign%20soil%2C%20damaging%20their%20reputation.%20Can%20one%20imagine%20how%20India%E2%80%99s%20intel%20and%20information%20sharing%20architecture%20with%20its%20democratic%20allies%20and%20partners%20may%20be%20disrupted%20after%20an%20episode%20like%20this%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20previous%20article%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Findia-g20-economy-world-domestic-outlook%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethis%20author%20argued%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cspan%3Ehow%20India%E2%80%99s%20paradoxical%20world%20outlook%20and%20waning%20moral%20stature%20in%20conduct%20on%20multilateral%20(and%20some%20bilateral)%20issues%2C%20cannot%20be%20enveloped%20nor%20hidden%20in%20some%20%E2%80%98green%20tented%20sheet%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20US%20indictment%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ealso%20hints%20at%20what%20may%20have%20informed%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EJustin%20Trudeau%E2%80%99s%20sensational%20September%202023%20statement%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20there%20were%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Ccredible%20allegations%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20linking%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20the%20murder%20of%20another%20Khalistan%20activist.%20While%20Ottawa%20has%20not%20revealed%20much%20in%20public%20%E2%80%93%20apparently%20to%20preserve%20the%20confidentiality%20of%20judicial%20proceedings%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fnijjar-pannun-modi-foreign-policy-national-interest%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%20piece%20published%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20says%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20%E2%80%9CCanadian%20officials%20had%20the%20Pannun%20case%20in%20mind%20and%20that%20at%20least%20some%20part%20of%20the%20intelligence%20linking%20India%20to%20Nijjar%20has%20come%20in%20the%20form%20of%20electronic%20messages%20the%20US%20has%20captured%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F30010249%2Findictment.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F30010249%2Findictment.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F30010249%2Findictment-300x150.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F30010249%2Findictment-1024x512.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F30010249%2Findictment-800x400.jpg%20800w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-687016%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EGurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun%2C%20a%20still%20image%20ofthe%20Advance%20Payment%20as%20shown%20in%20the%20DoJ%20indictment%20of%20Nikhil%20Gupta%2C%20and%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20have%20now%20seen%20at%20least%20two%20instances%20of%20charges%20by%20India%E2%80%99s%20democratic%20allies%20and%20partners%20of%20not%20being%20%E2%80%98honest%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98truthful%E2%80%99%20to%20its%20global%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emoral%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Estanding.%20In%20India%E2%80%99s%20own%20amoral%2C%20apathetic%20exceptionalism%2C%20there%20is%20also%20a%20silent%20embrace%20of%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20assassin%20Nathuram%20Godse%2C%20and%20his%20(Godse%E2%80%99s)%20ideological%20disposition%2C%20as%20against%20an%20embrace%20of%20Gandhian%20ideals%20of%20peace%20and%20non-violence%20which%20made%20India%20globally%20recognised%20and%20respected%20by%20all%20powers%20across%20the%20globe.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20also%20buffoonish%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20foreign%20policy%20ecosystem%20to%20believe%20it%20enjoys%20an%20undistilled%20faith%20amongst%20the%20(still)%20powerful%20G7%20countries%20if%20the%20tools%20for%20channelising%20instruments%20of%20economic%20integration%20operate%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Esans%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20basic%20domestic%20prerequisites%20of%20realised%20social%20cohesion%3B%20a%20safeguarded%20rights-based%20constitutional%20order%2C%20ensured%20by%20the%20separation%20of%20powers.%20India%20can%20hardly%20compromise%20on%20these%20prerequisites%20if%20it%20is%20serious%20about%20playing%20a%20more%20important%20role%20in%20a%20complex%2C%20multi-polar%20world.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fnijjar-pannun-modi-foreign-policy-national-interest%5C%22%3EFrom%20Nijjar%20to%20Pannun%2C%20Modi%20Government%E2%80%99s%20Recklessness%20is%20Undermining%20National%20Interest%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20West%E2%80%99s%20more%20accommodative%20position%20on%20a%20number%20of%20contested%20issues%20%E2%80%93%20India%E2%80%99s%20position%20on%20the%20Israel-Palestine%20conflict%2C%20the%20Ukraine-Russia%20war%2C%20or%20on%20domestic%20issues%20like%20human%20rights%2C%20minority%20protection%2C%20and%20freedom%20of%20press%20%E2%80%93%20is%20rather%20explained%20by%20their%20greater%20contempt%20for%20an%20authoritarian%20China%20under%20Xi%20Jinping%2C%20than%20say%2C%20a%20need%20for%20developing%20bonhomie%20with%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENew%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20%E2%80%93%20amidst%20a%20rising%2C%20ideological%20wave%20of%20Hindutva%20%E2%80%93%20embraces%20Godse%E2%80%99s%20violence%20and%20an%20eye%20for%20an%20eye%20vengeance-seeking%20mindset.%20This%20has%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailyo.in%2Fvariety%2Fgeorge-floyd-breonna-taylor-racism-in-usa-anti-caa-nrc-protests-social-justice-polarisation-33154%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Enothing%20to%20do%20with%20social%20justice%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EJustice%20isn%E2%80%99t%20about%20seeking%20vengeance%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20or%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Erevenge%20%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thequint.com%2Fopinion%2Fisrael-palestine-need-for-transcendental-justice-in-a-world-marred-by-conflict-conquest%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eit%20is%20much%20more%20than%20that%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEmbracing%20violence%20and%20violent%20means%20of%20institutional%20propriety%2C%20and%20an%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thequint.com%2Fopinion%2Fisrael-palestine-need-for-transcendental-justice-in-a-world-marred-by-conflict-conquest%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eapathetic%20conduct%20towards%20peace%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20own%20domestic%20and%20subsequently%20international%20position%2C%20may%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20make%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20image%20regress%2C%20or%20fall%20into%20the%20same%20category%20of%20authoritarian%20nation-states%20(or%20%E2%80%98illiberal%20democracies%E2%80%99).%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECollective%20self-interest%20is%20difficult%20to%20realise%20by%20an%20independently%20motivated%20self-interested%20state%20of%20individuals%20unless%20each%20state%20has%20some%20form%20of%20assurance%20that%20others%20will%20conform%20if%20it%20does.%20And%20that%20assurance%20requires%20the%20external%20incentive%20provided%20by%20the%20sovereign%2C%20who%20sees%20to%20it%20that%20individual%20and%20collective%20self-interest%20coincide.%20It%20is%20critical%20for%20any%20nation%20(including%20India)%20to%20realise%20this.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findias-abstention-in-un-gaza-truce-vote-reflects-amoral-apathetic-exceptionalism%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20founding%20editor%20argued%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20security%20history%20has%20been%20known%20to%20arm%20and%20train%20the%20Liberation%20Tigers%20of%20Tamil%20Eelam%20in%20Sri%20Lanka%3B%20and%20launching%20%E2%80%98surgical%20strikes%E2%80%99%20on%20alleged%20terrorist%20sites%20inside%20Pakistan-controlled%20territory.%20But%2C%20India%20has%20never%20so%20far%20been%20associated%20with%20targeted%20assassinations%20abroad.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ENew%20Delhi%20has%20shown%20no%20appetite%20for%20physically%20targeting%20wanted%20men%20or%20opponents%20overseas%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Enot%20necessarily%20beacuse%20of%20the%20lack%20of%20capability%20but%20a%20realistic%20political%20calculation%20about%20the%20associated%20risks%20and%20benefits.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20the%20current%20US%20indictment%20and%20the%20recklessness%20with%20which%20India%20responded%20to%20Trudeau%E2%80%99s%20allegations%20have%20done%20is%20put%20not%20just%20the%20current%20government%20but%20India%E2%80%99s%20own%20image%20and%20global%20position%20in%20the%20international%20security%20arena%2C%20in%20a%20more%20vulnerable%20position.%20It%20may%20cause%20more%20distance%20to%20be%20observed%20by%20democratic%20allies.%20Preferring%20Godse%20over%20Gandhi%20has%20a%20cost%2C%20not%20just%20in%20terms%20of%20an%20ideological%2C%20political%20disposition%2C%20but%20also%20from%20the%20perspective%20of%20foreign%20policy%20and%20how%20the%20world%20perceives%20the%20country%20in%20the%20near%20(and%20far%20future).%20Any%20Indian%20government%20and%20its%20leadership%20would%20be%20wise%20to%20recognise%20this.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fdeepanshu-mohan%5C%22%3EDeepanshu%20Mohan%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20associate%20profe