mesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fanimal-vs-sam-bahadur-lagaan-vs-gadar-biggest-bollywood-clashes-at-the-box-office%2Fphotostory%2F105628713.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105628713.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fanimal-vs-sam-bahadur-lagaan-vs-gadar-biggest-bollywood-clashes-at-the-box-office%2Fphotostory%2F105628713.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Democratic%20India%2C%20Why%20Was%20Statue%20of%20Manu%20Installed%20in%20a%20Court%20Before%20Ambedkar%E2%80%99s%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F08%2F16155753%2FManu-Rajasthan-HC.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20November%2026%2C%202023%2C%20a%20nine-foot-tall%20statue%20of%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%20was%20installed%20in%20the%20premises%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20Constitution%20Day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIronically%2C%20the%20architect%20of%20the%20Indian%20constitution%20had%20to%20wait%20for%2075%20years%20after%20independence%20for%20a%20statue%20to%20be%20erected%20in%20his%20honour.%20All%20this%20while%2C%20a%20taller%20statue%20of%20Manu%20(11%20feet)%20%E2%80%93%20whose%20teachings%20are%20against%20the%20basic%20structure%20and%20values%20of%20the%20constitution%20%E2%80%93%20was%20unveiled%20on%20the%20premises%20of%20the%20Jaipur%20bench%20of%20the%20Rajasthan%20high%20court%20way%20back%20in%201989.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%201970s%2C%20veteran%20Ambedkarite%20leader%20Dadasaheb%20Gaikwad%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.themooknayak.com%2Findia%2Fconstitution-month-special-dr-ambedkars-statue-to-grace-supreme-court-after-76-years-of-independence%5C%22%3Estarted%20his%20efforts%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20push%20for%20the%20installation%20of%20Ambedkar%E2%80%99s%20statue%20within%20the%20parliament%20complex.%20It%20was%20given%20heed%20only%20after%2056%20years.%20In%20contrast%2C%20it%20took%20hardly%2023%20days%20to%20install%20Manu%E2%80%99s%20statue%20in%20the%20Rajasthan%20high%20court%2C%20similar%20to%20the%20implementation%20of%20reservation%20for%20the%20Economically%20Weaker%20Sections%20(EWS)%20among%20the%20upper%20castes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prompt%20installation%20of%20the%20statue%20of%20Manu%20and%20the%20reluctance%20towards%20Ambedkar%20can%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20metaphor%20for%20the%20polity%20and%20society%20of%20post-independent%20India%2C%20which%20seems%20to%20show%20a%20continuity%20rather%20than%20a%20rupture%20after%201947.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20story%20of%20the%20existence%20of%20Manu%E2%80%99s%20statue%20can%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20glorification%20of%20undemocratic%20and%20oppressive%20Brahmanical%20values%2C%20sustaining%20all%20weathers%2C%20institutions%2C%20and%20governments%20of%20democratic%20India%2C%20which%20is%20slowly%20substituting%20Ambedkar%20from%20within.%20This%20is%20also%20a%20story%20of%20the%20victory%20of%20Manu%E2%80%99s%20India%20over%20the%20vision%20Ambedkar%20aspired%20for%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F30182411%2Fimage-1559.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221006%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F30182411%2Fimage-1559.png%201006w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F30182411%2Fimage-1559-300x243.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-687134%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22815%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EB.R.%20Ambedkar%E2%80%99s%20statue%20in%20the%20premises%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India.%20Photo%3A%20X%40ambedkariteIND%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EManu%E2%80%99s%20Bar%20and%20Bench%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2010%2C%201989%2C%20Padam%20Kumar%20Jain%2C%20the%20president%20of%20the%20Rajasthan%20High%20Court%20Officers%E2%80%99%20Association%2C%20proposed%20installing%20Manu%E2%80%99s%20statue%20in%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20premises%20as%20part%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Cbeautification%20plan%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20beautification%20was%20the%20goal%2C%20why%20didn%E2%80%99t%20Jain%20consider%20an%20Ambedkar%20statue%2C%20is%20an%20irrelevant%20question.%20Immediately%2C%20just%2023%20days%20after%20this%20proposal%2C%20on%20March%203%2C%201989%2C%20the%20proposal%20was%20approved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20that%20time%2C%20Shiv%20Charan%20Mathur%20of%20the%20Congress%20was%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Rajasthan%3B%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20was%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20and%20Justice%20E.S.%20Venkataramiah%20was%20the%20chief%20justice%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20didn%E2%80%99t%20this%20move%20seem%20objectionable%20to%20any%20of%20them%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20opposition%20to%20the%20installation%20of%20Manu%E2%80%99s%20statue%20%E2%80%93%20which%20was%20considered%20a%20stain%20on%20the%20dignity%20and%20values%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20Dalits%2C%20women%2C%20Shudras%20and%20working%20classes%20%E2%80%93%20the%20awakened%20Dalit%20community%20slowly%20began%20to%20protest.%20Hence%2C%20on%20July%2028%2C%201989%2C%20a%20full%20court%20sitting%20of%20the%20Rajasthan%20high%20court%20unanimously%20decided%20to%20remove%20the%20statue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20immediately%2C%20Acharya%20Dharmendra%2C%20a%20leader%20of%20the%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20(VHP)%2C%20filed%20a%20public%20interest%20litigation%20(PIL)%20against%20it.%20The%20high%20court%20quickly%20accepted%20this%20PIL%20for%20hearing%2C%20and%20in%20August%201989%2C%20a%20stay%20order%20was%20issued%20against%20its%20own%20full%20sitting.%20Not%20only%20that%2C%20it%20also%20instructed%20that%20any%20further%20hearings%20in%20this%20case%20should%20be%20conducted%20only%20by%20a%20division%20bench%2C%20including%20the%20chief%20justice%20of%20the%20high%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20the%20stay%20order%20and%20Manu%E2%80%99s%20statue%20have%20remained%20on%20the%20premises%20of%20the%20high%20court.%20And%20the%20case%20itself%20has%20acquired%20the%20notoriety%20of%20the%20longest%20pending%20PIL%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20Rajasthan%20high%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20recent%20hearing%20on%20this%20case%20happened%20in%202015.%20Over%20300%20Brahmin%20and%20%E2%80%98upper%E2%80%99%20caste%20lawyers%20had%20rushed%20from%20various%20courts%20to%20attend%20the%20hearing.%20As%20A.K.%20Jain%2C%20an%20advocate%20for%20the%20Dalit%20groups%2C%20tried%20to%20draw%20the%20judges%E2%80%99%20attention%20to%20the%20anti-Dalit%2C%20Shudra%20and%20women%20verses%20in%20Manusmriti%2C%20these%20%E2%80%98upper%E2%80%99%20caste%20lawyers%20started%20a%20commotion%20inside%20the%20court%20premises%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20postponement%20of%20the%20hearing.%20It%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.outlookindia.com%2Fnational%2Fambedkar-jayanti-manu-statue-in-rajasthan-high-court-and-dalit-activists-long-demand-to-remove-it-news-191517%5C%22%3Ehas%20not%20been%20resumed%3C%2Fa%3E%20since.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meantime%2C%20several%20Dalit%20organisations%20and%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20leaders%20have%20been%20demanding%20the%20removal%20of%20Manu%E2%80%99s%20statue.%20On%20October%208%2C%202018%2C%20two%20Ambedkarite%20women%20activists%20from%20Aurangabad%2C%20Maharashtra%20%E2%80%93%20Sheelabai%20Pawar%20and%20Kanta%20Ramesh%20Ahire%20%E2%80%93%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fkantabai-ahire-sheela-pawar-manu-statue-blackened-protest%5C%22%3E%20were%20arrested%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20throwing%20black%20paint%20on%20Manu%E2%80%99s%20statue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20nothing%20could%20remove%20Manu%E2%80%99s%20statue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmanusmriti-hindu-rashtra-rss%5C%22%3EThe%20Laws%20of%20Manu%20and%20What%20They%20Would%20Mean%20for%20Citizens%20of%20the%20Hindu%20Rashtra%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Rajasthan%2C%20governments%20alternate%20between%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20in%20every%20election.%20The%20BJP%20and%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%E2%80%99s%20stance%20has%20often%20justified%20the%20caste%20system.%20However%2C%20why%20didn%E2%80%99t%20the%20Congress%20party%2C%20which%20claims%20to%20be%20pro-constitution%2C%20put%20its%20weight%20behind%20the%20litigation%20to%20remove%20Manu%E2%80%99s%20statue%20when%20it%20came%20to%20power%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20answer%20lies%20in%20a%20statement%20by%20Congress%20leader%20and%20head%20of%20its%20manifesto%20drafting%20committee%2C%20Vibhuti%20Bhushan%20Sharma.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fa-day-in-the-life-of-a-manu-statue-in-the-rajasthan-high-court-5421545%2F%5C%22%3ESharma%2C%20a%20former%20president%20of%20the%20Rajasthan%20High%20Court%20Bar%20Association%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20statue%20of%20Manu%20was%20installed%20in%20the%20high%20court%2C%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20for%20any%20particular%20caste.%20Manu%20is%20regarded%20as%20the%20first%20person%20to%20have%20come%20up%20with%20a%20written%20law.%20If%20there%20is%20any%20downside%20to%20that%20law%2C%20it%20is%20open%20to%20amendments%20as%20is%20done%20in%20our%20constitution.%20The%20statue%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20associated%20with%20any%20caste.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20irony%20is%20this%20statement%20of%20the%20Congress%20leader%20resembles%20closely%20with%20the%20statement%20of%20VHP%E2%80%99s%20Acharya%20Dharmendra%2C%20who%20had%20filed%20a%20petition%20against%20the%20removal%20of%20Manu%E2%80%99s%20statue.%20He%20had%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20great%20idea%20to%20have%20a%20Manu%20statue%20inside%20the%20high%20court%20as%20he%20was%20the%20first%20person%20anywhere%20in%20the%20world%20to%20draft%20a%20law.%20Those%20who%20oppose%20him%20are%20ignorant%20of%20Manu%E2%80%99s%20philosophy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20is%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20understanding%20of%20Manu%20or%20the%20constitution%20different%20from%20the%20RSS%2C%20which%20claims%20Manusmriti%20to%20be%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20best%20constitution%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20there%20is%20any%20difference%2C%20isn%E2%80%99t%20it%20enough%20to%20preserve%20Ambedkar%E2%80%99s%20ideals%20and%20the%20constitution%20from%20the%20onslaught%20of%20Manu%2C%20the%20RSS%20and%20the%20BJP%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndifference%20of%20SC%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20has%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20responsible%20for%20protecting%20the%20constitution%2C%20done%20in%20this%20matter%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20case%20demanding%20the%20removal%20of%20Manu%E2%80%99s%20statue%20from%20the%20Rajasthan%20high%20court%20premises%20had%20been%20deliberately%20delayed%20for%20more%20than%2025%20years%2C%20several%20Dalit%20activists%20and%20organisations%20filed%20a%20PIL%20in%20the%20top%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20on%20February%2024%2C%202023%2C%20the%20division%20bench%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20comprising%20Justices%20Sanjeev%20Khanna%20and%20Justice%20Sundaresh%2C%20dismissed%20the%20petition%2C%20saying%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20do%20not%20find%20any%20good%20ground%20and%20reason%20to%20entertain%20the%20present%20writ%20petition%20as%20a%20public%20interest%20litigation%20under%20Article%2032%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20and%20hence%2C%20the%20writ%20petition%20is%20dismissed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20decision%20allowed%20Manu%E2%80%99s%20statue%20to%20remain.%20And%20the%20same%20court%20has%20unveiled%20the%20statue%20of%20Ambedkar%20on%20its%20own%20premises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManu%20and%20Manusmriti%20represent%20injustice%2C%20social%20inequality%2C%20caste%20hierarchy%2C%20and%20patriarchy.%20Ambedkar%20and%20the%20constitution%20stand%20for%20equality%2C%20compassion%2C%20socio-economic%20justice%2C%20and%20fraternity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20can%20both%20coexist%3F%20How%20can%20both%20be%20symbols%20of%20the%20Indian%20judiciary%20that%20is%20tasked%20with%20protecting%20the%20constitution%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hindutva%20forces%20have%20reinterpreted%20the%20constitution%20and%20the%20history%20to%20suit%20the%20ideals%20of%20Manusmriti%20while%20at%20the%20same%20time%20idolising%20Ambedkar%2C%20They%20have%20perhaps%20made%20this%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fsymbols-serve-oppressors-that-is-why-manu-must-fall%5C%22%3ESymbols%20Serve%20Oppressors%2C%20That%20Is%20Why%20Manu%20Must%20Fall%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConstitution%20Day%20or%20Vedic%20Day%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20latest%20stratagem%20was%20last%20year%E2%80%99s%20order%20by%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20to%20celebrate%20November%2026%2C%20Constitution%20Adoption%20Day%2C%20around%20the%20theme%20of%20%E2%80%98India%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Mother%20of%20Democracy%E2%80%99.%20Along%20with%20this%20order%2C%20the%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Historical%20Research%20provided%20a%20conceptual%20note%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fdistorted-histories-inmother-of-democracy%5C%22%3Ewhich%20claimed%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20khap%20panchayats%20were%20institutions%20of%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20Ambedkar%2C%20in%20his%20work%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.in%2FANNIHILATION-CASTE-Annotated-Critical-AMBEDKAR%2Fdp%2F8189059637%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EAnnihilation%20of%20Caste%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20had%20given%20a%20call%20to%20destroy%20the%20Vedas%2C%20Puranas%2C%20and%20Manusmriti%2C%20if%20Hinduism%20were%20to%20truly%20become%20a%20religion%2C%20and%20if%20a%20Hindu%20were%20to%20become%20a%20genuine%20human%20being%2C%20and%20if%20India%20was%20to%20become%20a%20genuine%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFar%20from%20demolishing%20the%20ideals%20of%20Manusmriti%2C%20Manu%E2%80%99s%20statue%20stands%20on%20a%20court%20premises%20%E2%80%93%20with%20neither%20political%20parties%20nor%20the%20higher%20judiciary%20seemingly%20finding%20any%20contradiction%20in%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701354225000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F08%2F16155753%2FManu-Rajasthan-HC.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Findia-democracy-statue-manu-ambedkar%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20existence%20of%20Manu's%20statue%20on%20a%20court%20premises%20can%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20glorification%20of%20values%20that%20are%20against%20the%20basic%20structure%20and%20values%20of%20the%20constitution.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Findia-democracy-statue-manu-ambedkar%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bedouin%20family%20desperate%20for%20news%20on%20teenagers%20held%20hostage%20in%20Gaza%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701354138000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F79D4%2Fproduction%2F_131888113_bedouinhostagescomposite.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67573069%22%2C%22s