ed%20to%20ensuring%20fast-paced%20growth%20to%20create%20more%20opportunities%2C%20rapid%20eradication%20of%20poverty%20and%20improving%20'ease%20of%20living'%20for%20our%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20PM%20Modi%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20National%20Statistical%20Office%20(NSO)%20data%2C%20the%20agriculture%20sector%20GVA%20(Gross%20Value%20Added)%20growth%20decelerated%20to%201.2%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20September%202023%20quarter%20from%202.5%20per%20cent%20a%20year%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20expansion%20in%20financial%2C%20real%20estate%20and%20professional%20services'%20GVA%20was%206%20per%20cent%2C%20down%20from%207.1%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20year-ago%20quarter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20GVA%20in%20the%20manufacturing%20sector%20showed%20a%20growth%20of%2013.9%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20second%20quarter%20of%20the%20current%20fiscal%20compared%20to%20a%20contraction%20of%203.8%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20year-ago%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20data%2C%20the%20output%20(GVA)%20in%20the%20'mining%20and%20quarrying'%20accelerated%20to%2010%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20second%20quarter%20against%20a%20contraction%20of%200.1%20per%20cent%20a%20year%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElectricity%2C%20gas%2C%20water%20supply%20and%20other%20utility%20services'%20grew%20by%2010.1%20per%20cent%20from%206.1%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20construction%20sector%20recorded%20a%20growth%20of%2013.3%20per%20cent%20year-on-year%20in%20the%20second%20quarter%20compared%20to%205.7%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20growth%20in%20gross%20domestic%20product%20(GDP)%20during%20the%20April-June%20quarter%20of%202023-24%20remained%20unchanged%20at%207.8%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BReal%20GDP%20or%20GDP%20at%20Constant%20(2011-12)%20Prices%20in%20Q2%202023-24%20is%20estimated%20to%20attain%20a%20level%20of%20Rs%2041.74%20lakh%20crore%2C%20as%20against%20Rs%2038.78%20lakh%20crore%20in%20Q2%202022-23%2C%20showing%20a%20growth%20of%207.6%20per%20cent%20as%20compared%20to%206.2%20per%20cent%20in%20Q2%202022-23%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20NSO%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENominal%20GDP%20or%20GDP%20at%20current%20prices%20in%20Q2%202023-24%20is%20estimated%20at%20Rs%2071.66%20lakh%20crore%20against%20Rs%2065.67%20lakh%20crore%20in%20Q2%202022-23%2C%20showing%20a%20growth%20of%209.1%20per%20cent%20as%20compared%20to%2017.2%20per%20cent%20in%20Q2%202022-23%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20further%20said%20the%20GDP%20at%20constant%20(2011-12)%20prices%20in%20April-September%202023-24%20(H1%202023-24)%20is%20estimated%20at%20Rs%2082.11%20lakh%20crore%20against%20Rs%2076.22%20lakh%20crore%20during%20the%20corresponding%20period%20of%20the%20previous%20year%2C%20showing%20a%20growth%20of%207.7%20per%20cent%20in%20H1%202023-24%20compared%20to%209.5%20per%20cent%20in%20H1%202022-23%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGDP%20at%20current%20prices%20in%20H1%202023-24%20is%20estimated%20at%20Rs%20142.33%20lakh%20crore%20compared%20to%20Rs%20131.09%20lakh%20crore%20during%20the%20corresponding%20period%20of%20the%20previous%20year%2C%20showing%20a%20growth%20of%208.6%20per%20cent%20in%20H1%202023-24%20against%2022.2%20per%20cent%20in%20H1%202022-23.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20output%20of%20eight%20key%20infrastructure%20sectors%20jumped%2012.1%20per%20cent%20in%20October%202023%20against%200.7%20per%20cent%20expansion%20in%20the%20year-ago%20period%20on%20account%20of%20a%20sharp%20uptick%20in%20production%20of%20coal%2C%20steel%2C%20cement%20and%20electricity%2C%20according%20to%20the%20official%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government's%20fiscal%20deficit%20at%20the%20end%20of%20October%20touched%2045%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20full-year%20budget%20estimate%2C%20according%20to%20data%20released%20by%20the%20Controller%20General%20of%20Accounts%20(CGA)%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%