20his%20contract%20length%20Dravid%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20announced%20officially%2C%20I%20haven't%20signed%20anything%20yet%2C%20let%20the%20papers%20come%20officially%20from%20the%20BCCI.%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBatting%20coach%20Vikram%20Rathour%2C%20fielding%20coach%20T%20Dilip%20and%20bowling%20coach%20Paras%20Mhambrey%20will%20continue%20their%20stint%20with%20Team%20India%20as%20BCCI%20also%20extended%20contracts%20of%20the%20support%20staff%20of%20Team%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDravid's%20second%20stint%20with%20Team%20India%20will%20be%20the%20tour%20of%20South%20Africa%20from%20December%2010%2C%20which%20will%20have%20three%20ODIs%20and%20T20Is%20each%20and%20two%20Tests.%20The%20red-ball%20leg%20will%20start%20from%20December%2026.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20that%20will%20be%20a%20five-match%20Test%20series%20against%20England%20at%20home%2C%20before%20the%20ICC%20T20%20World%20Cup%20in%20June%20in%20West%20Indies%2FUSA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDravid%20replaced%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ravi%20Shastri%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F41719-ravishankar-jayadritha-shastri-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERavi%20Shastri%3C%2Fa%3E%20following%20a%20disappointing%20ICC%20T20%20World%20Cup%20campaign%20in%202021%2C%20which%20saw%20India%20exit%20in%20the%20Super%2012%20stage.%20He%20was%20appointed%20for%20a%20two-year%20term%2C%20which%20ended%20with%20India's%20runners-up%20finish%20in%20the%20recently%20concluded%20ICC%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20announcement%20of%20the%20contract%20extension%2C%20Dravid%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20last%20two%20years%20with%20Team%20India%20have%20been%20thoroughly%20memorable.%20Together%2C%20we%20have%20witnessed%20the%20highs%20and%20lows%2C%20and%20throughout%20this%20journey%2C%20the%20support%20and%20camaraderie%20within%20the%20group%20have%20been%20phenomenal.%20I%20am%20genuinely%20proud%20of%20the%20culture%20we%20have%20set%20in%20the%20dressing%20room.%20It's%20a%20culture%20that%20stands%20resilient%2C%20whether%20in%20moments%20of%20triumph%20or%20adversity.%20The%20skills%20and%20talent%20that%20our%20team%20possesses%20are%20phenomenal%2C%20and%20what%20we've%20stressed%20is%20following%20the%20right%20process%20and%20sticking%20to%20our%20preparations%2C%20which%20has%20had%20a%20direct%20impact%20on%20the%20overall%20result.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20thank%20the%20BCCI%20and%20the%20Office%20Bearers%20for%20placing%20their%20trust%20in%20me%2C%20endorsing%20my%20vision%2C%20and%20providing%20support%20during%20this%20period.%20The%20demands%20of%20this%20role%20necessitate%20considerable%20time%20away%20from%20home%2C%20and%20I%20deeply%20appreciate%20my%20family's%20sacrifices%20and%20support.%20Their%20instrumental%20role%20behind%20the%20scenes%20has%20been%20invaluable.%20As%20we%20embrace%20new%20challenges%20post%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20we%20remain%20committed%20to%20the%20pursuit%20of%20excellence%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701350340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fu2vpmd8o_rahul-dravid-pc_625x300_20_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fhavent-signed-anything-rahul-dravid-on-indian-cricket-team-coaching-contract-duration-4621931%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rahul%20Dravid%20on%20Thursday%20stated%20that%20he%20hasn't%20signed%20any%20papers%20regarding%20the%20length%20of%20his%20contract%20extension%20with%20Team%20India%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fhavent-signed-anything-rahul-dravid-on-indian-cricket-team-coaching-contract-duration-4621931%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsp