0in%20Shillong%2C%20Nambie%E2%80%99s%20initiation%20to%20the%20kitchen%20started%20fairly%20young%20as%20her%20mother%20encouraged%20the%20children%20to%20make%20their%20own%20meals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20been%20cooking%20for%20as%20far%20as%20I%20can%20remember.%20My%20mother%20worked%20really%20hard%20to%20put%20food%20on%20the%20table.%20She%20would%20weave%20clothes%2C%20do%20embroidery%20and%20some%20small%20businesses.%20While%20she%20did%20this%20to%20provide%20us%20with%20a%20good%20life%2C%20she%20would%20make%20sure%20that%20we%20cooked%20our%20own%20meals%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nambie.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20after%20winning%20over%20top%20chefs%20%E2%80%94%20including%20British%20Chef%20Marco%20Pierre%20White%20%E2%80%94%20she%20says%20that%20she%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20so%20good%20at%20cooking!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20love%20to%20eat%20the%20most.%20I%20know%20how%20to%20cook%20but%20what%20I%20really%20enjoy%20is%20eating%20and%20finding%20new%20recipes%20in%20books%20and%20YouTube%20channels%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20she%20calls%20herself%20a%20%E2%80%9Crookie%20cook%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20foundation%20for%20her%20stint%20as%20a%20cook%20was%20strengthened%20in%20school%2C%20where%20she%20took%20home%20science%20as%20an%20elective%20subject.%20It%20was%20strengthened%20further%20when%20she%20started%20living%20by%20herself%20in%20Chennai%2C%20where%20she%20moved%20for%20her%20postgraduate%20studies%20and%20worked%20for%20a%20few%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20working%20as%20an%20assistant%20professor%20in%20a%20college%2C%20she%20also%20found%20time%20for%20her%20YouTube%20videos.%20She%20would%20go%20home%20during%20vacations%20and%20shoot%20videos%20every%20single%20day.%20Since%20her%20village%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20internet%20connectivity%2C%20she%20would%20edit%20and%20upload%20the%20videos%20after%20returning%20to%20Chennai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20her%20channel%2C%20she